Case Study Summary
Problem

The dataset contained inconsistent and missing values (e.g., UNKNOWN, ERROR, blank fields), 
making it difficult to analyze sales performance accurately.

Approach
Cleaned and standardized the dataset using Excel
Recalculated incorrect values (Quantity, Total Spent)
Handled missing categorical and date values
Performed exploratory data analysis using SQL
Built an interactive dashboard in Power BI

Key Findings
Salad is the highest revenue-generating product
Sales peaked in June, indicating seasonal demand
A large portion of transactions had missing payment and location data

Business Recommendations
Improve data collection systems to reduce “Unknown” values
Focus on high-performing products like Salad
Investigate seasonal trends to optimize inventory and marketing
